# Design Principles & Color System

Comprehensive design guidelines to maintain visual consistency and brand identity across the GoddessGPT application.

## Brand Identity

### Primary Brand Color
- **Main Brand Color**: `#A875D6` (Supportive Lavender)
- **Usage**: Primary buttons, highlights, brand elements, interactive states
- **Variations**:
  - Hover state: `#905fbf`
  - Light background: `bg-[#A875D6]/5`, `bg-[#A875D6]/10`, `bg-[#A875D6]/20`
  - Borders: `border-[#A875D6]/10`, `border-[#A875D6]/20`, `border-[#A875D6]/30`

### Color System (CSS Variables)
Follow the established color tokens defined in `src/index.css`:

**Light Theme Variables:**
- `--background: 0 0% 100%` (Pure white)
- `--foreground: 240 10% 3.9%` (Dark blue-gray)
- `--primary: 240 5.9% 10%` (Very dark blue)
- `--secondary: 240 4.8% 95.9%` (Light gray)
- `--muted: 240 4.8% 95.9%` (Light gray)
- `--accent: 240 4.8% 95.9%` (Light gray)
- `--destructive: 0 84.2% 60.2%` (Bright red)
- `--border: 240 5.9% 90%` (Light gray)

**Dark Theme Variables:**
- `--background: 240 10% 3.9%` (Dark blue-gray)
- `--foreground: 0 0% 98%` (Off-white)
- Complete dark theme support with proper contrast ratios

## Typography

### Font Family
- **Primary**: Inter (Google Fonts)
- **Usage**: All text content across the application
- **Weights**: Regular (400), Medium (500), Semibold (600), Bold (700)

### **STANDARDIZED** Typography Scale
**Consistent font sizes across ALL pages aligned with chat window standards for maximum consistency:**

#### Universal Typography Standards
**These sizes MUST be used consistently across Community, AI Assistant, Resources, Calendar, and ALL pages:**

- **Page/Section Headers**: `text-lg font-semibold text-black` (Main sections, card headers, dialog titles)
- **Primary Content Text**: `text-sm font-semibold text-black` (Names, titles, primary labels)
- **Secondary Content Text**: `text-sm` (Descriptions, body text, card descriptions)
- **Supporting/Meta Text**: `text-xs` (Timestamps, captions, helper text, metadata)
- **Muted Text**: Use `text-muted-foreground` class for secondary information

#### **CRITICAL COLOR RULE**
**All titles across cards and pages MUST be black in color unless explicitly stated otherwise:**
- **Page Headers**: `text-black` (not brand color)
- **Card Titles**: `text-black` (not brand color)
- **Dialog Titles**: `text-black` (not brand color)
- **Section Headers**: `text-black` (not brand color)
- **Form Labels**: `text-black` (not brand color)
- **Button Text**: `text-black` (not brand color)

#### Specific Applications
- **Page Headers**: `text-lg font-semibold text-black` (Community, Resources, Profile pages)
- **Post Titles**: `text-sm font-semibold text-black` (Community feed, resource cards)
- **User Names**: `text-sm font-semibold text-black` (Community listings, chat participants)
- **Email/Details**: `text-xs text-muted-foreground` (Contact details, metadata)
- **Timestamps**: `text-xs text-muted-foreground` (All timestamp displays)
- **Card Titles**: `text-lg font-semibold text-black` (Settings cards, notification cards)
- **Form Labels**: `text-sm font-medium text-black` (All form inputs)
- **Button Text**: `text-sm font-medium text-black` (All button labels)

#### Icons Aligned with Text
- **Section Header Icons**: `h-4 w-4` (alongside `text-lg` headers)
- **Content Icons**: `h-3.5 w-3.5` (alongside `text-sm` content)
- **Small Icons**: `h-3 w-3` (alongside `text-xs` metadata)

